    "contentHtml": "<p>The portfolio is finally out and running on a website with my alias on it. That is a big win!</p>\n<p>Moving forward, I have three main things to tackle every day. First, I need to revise my cybersecurity concepts. I have to start applying for off-campus jobs in a few months. They might remember the name GarryMarkus from the past, so that is a plus. Second, my chess skills are getting worse. They are not as good as they were when I was in 10th and 11th grade, so I need time to get them back on track. Third, I need to learn DSA. Google will not accept me without it, will they? I actually have to explain my code to them, or <mark>I can just joke that I copied GarryMarkus from some website! :)</mark></p>\n<p><img src=\"/attachments/2026-06-27/cmd%20ss.png\" alt=\"cmd ss.png\"></p>\n<p>When the day started, I had these targets:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p><mark><strong>Cybersecurity:</strong></mark> Study the Internet and IP Addresses. I have a lot of topics to cover, but I wanted to complete this unit today and maybe upload the final notes to my repository.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><mark><strong>Chess:</strong></mark> Practice Modern Defense lines, King and Pawn endgames, and look at some middlegame concepts.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><mark><strong>DSA:</strong></mark> Study this properly for the first time. I wanted to practice on online platforms and learn about Time and Space Complexity.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><mark><strong>Planning:</strong></mark> Make plans for tomorrow.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>I also had a chess class to teach today. I was planning to start with game analysis and then jump to the Caro-Kann. After that, the goal was to work on the frontend of the EnPassant website.</p>\n<p>But things changed. In the middle of working, I got the idea to redesign my portfolio again. And then, another redesign of the portfolio page happened just now!</p>\n<p><img src=\"/attachments/2026-06-27/Pasted%20image%2020260627154911.png\" alt=\"Pasted image 20260627154911.png\"></p>\n<p>I ended up giving my whole day to the portfolio and the EnPassant website. I was only able to give about 1.5 hours to cybersecurity. </p>\n<p><img src=\"/attachments/2026-06-27/Screenshot%202026-06-28%20014934.png\" alt=\"Screenshot 2026-06-28 014934.png\"></p>\n<p>My chess class also got pushed to tomorrow. That means <mark>I have to teach 3 classes tomorrow!</mark> I feel really good about coaching 3 students, but what about my other studies? I guess we will see how that goes tomorrow.</p>\n<p>I might not be sleeping tonight. But the good thing is, the new redesign is done and the portfolio is going to be live now. New look, new theme!</p>\n<p><img src=\"/attachments/2026-06-27/Pasted%20image%2020260628015153.png\" alt=\"Pasted image 20260628015153.png\"></p>\n"
